<!-- Showcase Area -->
<div id="showcase">
<div class="container">
<div class="showcase-content">
<h2><i>Learning System of Technology</i></h2>
<p class="lead">
    A learning system is essentially a collection of artefacts that are ‘brought together’, in an appropriate way, in order to create an environment that will facilitate various types of learning process. Learning system s can take a variety of different forms - for example, a book, a mobile form, a computer, an online forum, a school and a university.
</p>
<a href="#" class="btn">Read More</a>
</div>
